<div class="project-text">
    <h3>The Project</h3>
    <p>Two friends I have known forever. Years ago they got into 3D design and printing, first as a hobby, then as a proper job. Today they run a physical shop, sell models on all the main platforms in the field, and manage a social page with a big enough following to bring in sponsorships and collaborations on the regular.</p>
    <p>I have been involved in their image, physical and digital, since before they even had a name. The naming was part of it too. They used to be Hikikomori3D.</p>
